<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Apr1927"><font color="red">28 April 1927</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I may leave Paris next week as I have ceased working and sent all manuscript out of the house. What name or names would you give <font face="wake">N</font>? </div>
